'''Roger Bates''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Awards===

* [[Mott-Smith Trophy]] (3) 1975, 1988, 1992

===Wins===

* [[Senior Bowl (bridge)|d'Orsi Senior Bowl]] (4) 2003, 2005, 2007, 2013 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[Rosenblum Cup]] (2) 1994, 2006 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-open-teams.aspx Rosenblum Cup Winners]</ref>

* [[Cavendish Invitational|Cavendish Invitational Pairs]] (1) 1980 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (12)
